1. Project name:
Piras Luxury Resort

2. Description
A professional, modern, and fully responsive luxury resort landing page built from scratch. This project showcases foundational frontend web development skills, semantic structure design, dynamic data population by using Tailwind CSS and JavaScript.

3. Key Feature
- Responsive Web Design : layout optimized seamlessly for Mobile, Tablet, and Desktop screens using Tailwind CSS utilities.
- Dark Mode Feature: Smooth theme swapping between light and navy-dark modes with persistent local storage tracking.
- Dynamic Content Rendering: JavaScript-driven injection mapping for luxury suite cards.
- Form Validation: Client-side JavaScript validation logic handling real-time error notifications on the reservation channel.
- Smooth Navigation: Working navigation links with modern CSS scroll behavior.

4. Technologies used 
- HTML5: Semantic tags for clean layout structures.
- Tailwind CSS (CDN): Utility-first framework for an advanced modern design system and adaptive grid.
- FontAwesome & Icons: Vector graphics and typography icons.
- JavaScript (ES6): Logic engine for dynamic rendering, theme state caching, and security error checking.
- Git & GitHub: Version control setup.
- Vercel: Cloud host production deployment.

